// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2990 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: de0fcfda-83dd-5b6f-ba14-63a895ecc142

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.10*")
